@startuml
autonumber
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
    ParticipantBorderColor #E67E22
}

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Admin Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "Report API" as API
participant "Aggregation Service" as Stats
database "SQL Server" as DB

Admin -> Dashboard: Access Reports Page
Dashboard -> API: GET /api/v1/stats/sales-summary
API -> Stats: Compute Monthly Revenue
Stats -> DB: SUM(TotalAmount) FROM Orders...
DB --> Stats: Raw Data
Stats -> Stats: Format Data for Chart (JSON)
Stats --> API: Stats Report DTO
API --> Dashboard: Render Charts (Chart.js/MudBlazor)
@enduml